My turn!
Here, catch it!

38:25.966 --> 38:27.050
Mine!

38:40.981 --> 38:42.941
Ivar, do you want to play?

38:49.406 --> 38:50.490
Got it!

38:53.118 --> 38:54.912
It's mine, give it back!

38:56.246 --> 38:57.623
Now you go!

38:59.124 --> 39:00.500
Here! To me!

39:04.671 --> 39:05.714
Throw it!

39:06.965 --> 39:08.008
Here!

39:08.508 --> 39:09.885
Give it here!

39:13.513 --> 39:15.432
- Not to him.
- No, you...

39:15.515 --> 39:16.558
Higher!

39:18.518 --> 39:20.103
My turn!

39:20.187 --> 39:21.230
To me!

39:27.778 --> 39:29.363
Come on! Here!

39:56.390 --> 39:57.641
Do not be afraid.

39:58.600 --> 39:59.893
It's not your fault.

39:59.977 --> 40:01.853
Everything is all right.

40:05.023 --> 40:07.234
Everything will be all right.

40:56.575 --> 40:57.909
What is that?

41:00.620 --> 41:01.955
Can I see?

41:05.917 --> 41:07.210
Where did you find this?

41:07.294 --> 41:09.004
I took it from someone.

41:09.629 --> 41:10.797
Why are you so interested?

41:13.842 --> 41:15.343
I want to talk to you.

41:15.761 --> 41:17.137
What about?

41:18.513 --> 41:19.598
Us.

41:20.974 --> 41:23.518
We have moments
when I feel so close to you,

41:23.643 --> 41:24.978
especially when
you're inside me,

41:25.103 --> 41:26.438
but then you
don't want to talk,

41:26.521 --> 41:28.231
and I wonder why
you really came for me

41:28.356 --> 41:30.025
and took me
away from my child.

41:37.532 --> 41:38.658
Torvi.

41:44.456 --> 41:45.999
I talk to you.

42:03.183 --> 42:04.559
By the way,

42:05.519 --> 42:06.895
that was Erlendur's ring.

42:11.066 --> 42:13.693
He got it from his father,
King Horik.

42:55.360 --> 42:59.114
You look... Lagertha,
you look so beautiful.

43:03.076 --> 43:05.745
This is always how I imagined
this moment.

43:06.913 --> 43:08.540
Wherever I am,

43:08.623 --> 43:12.544
I don't ever want to forget
how you looked on
our wedding day.

